name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 43: Halloween Haunts

content.html:
Dear Internet, This week is our Halloween special! We have three spooky questions for you. We chat about a haunted doll, when is it too soon to invite your girlfriend who you’ve been hanging out with for 7 months to your families casual Halloween party, and being haunted by a tune. The doll in question: https://imgur.com/UMAhwhD Stay gold, XOXO We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
